Text.SourceString: Ah, seeker of the jungle's heart, you tread upon ancient paths.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, seeker of the jungle's heart, you tread upon ancient paths.

Text.SourceString: To understand the jungle, one must listen to the whisper of leaves and the murmur of streams.//For in every breath of wind, a story is told.
Text.LocalizedString: To understand the jungle, one must listen to the whisper of leaves and the murmur of streams.//For in every breath of wind, a story is told.

Text.SourceString: Hoo-hoo-hoo!
Text.LocalizedString: Hoo-hoo-hoo!

Text.SourceString: Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!
Text.LocalizedString: Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!

Text.SourceString: My small friend... The jungle holds mysteries deep as its roots. Seek with respect, and its secrets it shares.//Hoo-hoo-hoo!
Text.LocalizedString: My small friend... The jungle holds mysteries deep as its roots. Seek with respect, and its secrets it shares.//Hoo-hoo-hoo!

Text.SourceString: Beware the allure of the jungle's heart. It gives bountifully, yet demands reverence in return.
Text.LocalizedString: Beware the allure of the jungle's heart. It gives bountifully, yet demands reverence in return.

Text.SourceString: Guardians of the green, we are. To protect these woods, a duty noble and true.
Text.LocalizedString: Guardians of the green, we are. To protect these woods, a duty noble and true.

Text.SourceString: Hoo-hoo-hoo!
Text.LocalizedString: Hoo-hoo-hoo!

Text.SourceString: Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!
Text.LocalizedString: Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!

Text.SourceString: Long ago, trees walked and talked like men. Their ancient wisdom still echoes if you hear closely.
Text.LocalizedString: Long ago, trees walked and talked like men. Their ancient wisdom still echoes if you hear closely.

Text.SourceString: Many have sought the legendary fish, a being of light and shadow, swimming in the depths of our sacred waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Many have sought the legendary fish, a being of light and shadow, swimming in the depths of our sacred waters.

Text.SourceString: The legendary fish, a prize for those who understand the jungle's rhythm. Perhaps, in your hands, it may find its match.
Text.LocalizedString: The legendary fish, a prize for those who understand the jungle's rhythm. Perhaps, in your hands, it may find its match.

Text.SourceString: In you, a unique destiny unfolds. Cast your line with respect, and the legendary fish might grace you with its presence.
Text.LocalizedString: In you, a unique destiny unfolds. Cast your line with respect, and the legendary fish might grace you with its presence.

Text.SourceString: What journey, dear traveler, brings you to these verdant depths? Seek you knowledge or adventure?
Text.LocalizedString: What journey, dear traveler, brings you to these verdant depths? Seek you knowledge or adventure?

Text.SourceString: From distant lands, you come.//Your eyes, my small friend, they hold a quest unspoken. Pray, reveal your heart's true seeking.
Text.LocalizedString: From distant lands, you come.//Your eyes, my small friend, they hold a quest unspoken. Pray, reveal your heart's true seeking.

Text.SourceString: As leaves fall and rot, so new life springs. Such is the eternal dance of creation.
Text.LocalizedString: As leaves fall and rot, so new life springs. Such is the eternal dance of creation.

Text.SourceString: Ooo-ooo-ooo!
Text.LocalizedString: Ooo-ooo-ooo!

Text.SourceString: Soft rain, a blessing from the sky, nurturing the heart of our home.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!
Text.LocalizedString: Soft rain, a blessing from the sky, nurturing the heart of our home.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!

Text.SourceString: Listen to the rain's song, traveler. In each drop, a story of the jungle's soul.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!
Text.LocalizedString: Listen to the rain's song, traveler. In each drop, a story of the jungle's soul.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!

Text.SourceString: Storms, mighty in their fury, remind us of the untamed power of nature.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!
Text.LocalizedString: Storms, mighty in their fury, remind us of the untamed power of nature.//Ooo-ooo-ooo!

Text.SourceString: Fear not the tempest's rage; within its wild heart lies the strength of the jungle.//Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!
Text.LocalizedString: Fear not the tempest's rage; within its wild heart lies the strength of the jungle.//Hoo-hoo-hoo-HAA-HAA!

Text.SourceString: The Winter's slumber brings a time of reflection, a moment for the jungle to pause and renew.
Text.LocalizedString: The Winter's slumber brings a time of reflection, a moment for the jungle to pause and renew.

Text.SourceString: Beneath the cool Winter canopy, life continues in subtle ways, unseen but ever present.
Text.LocalizedString: Beneath the cool Winter canopy, life continues in subtle ways, unseen but ever present.

Text.SourceString: The cool waters bring a different rhythm to the jungle.
Text.LocalizedString: The cool waters bring a different rhythm to the jungle.

Text.SourceString: The rivers now whisper with a cooler breath, my small friend.
Text.LocalizedString: The rivers now whisper with a cooler breath, my small friend.

Text.SourceString: The warmth of summer brings forth a bounty of fruits and flowers, a feast for the eyes and the spirit.
Text.LocalizedString: The warmth of summer brings forth a bounty of fruits and flowers, a feast for the eyes and the spirit.

Text.SourceString: The days stretch long and full of light.
Text.LocalizedString: The days stretch long and full of light.

Text.SourceString: Ah, the water is warm, bathe, traveler. Let the jungle's embrace refresh your spirit.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, the water is warm, bathe, traveler. Let the jungle's embrace refresh your spirit.

Text.SourceString: In the heart of the jungle, every whisper of the wind and rustle of leaves tells a story.//Listen closely, and the jungle will speak to you.
Text.LocalizedString: In the heart of the jungle, every whisper of the wind and rustle of leaves tells a story.//Listen closely, and the jungle will speak to you.

Text.SourceString: I watch over these lands, not as a ruler over subjects, but as a guardian of the delicate balance of life.
Text.LocalizedString: I watch over these lands, not as a ruler over subjects, but as a guardian of the delicate balance of life.

Text.SourceString: Even the mightiest tree in the jungle once started as a tiny seed. So too do great things begin with small beginnings.
Text.LocalizedString: Even the mightiest tree in the jungle once started as a tiny seed. So too do great things begin with small beginnings.

Text.SourceString: You walk on two small legs, a rare sight in my jungle. Yet, you move with care.
Text.LocalizedString: You walk on two small legs, a rare sight in my jungle. Yet, you move with care.

Text.SourceString: Your curiosity reminds me of the young monkeys here. Always exploring, always learning.
Text.LocalizedString: Your curiosity reminds me of the young monkeys here. Always exploring, always learning.

Text.SourceString: Humans are not common in these parts. Your presence here is interesting.
Text.LocalizedString: Humans are not common in these parts. Your presence here is interesting.

Text.SourceString: You're a human, not used to the jungle's ways, yet you try to understand. This is commendable.
Text.LocalizedString: You're a human, not used to the jungle's ways, yet you try to understand. This is commendable.

Text.SourceString: You look different from the creatures here, but you show respect for the jungle. That's good.
Text.LocalizedString: You look different from the creatures here, but you show respect for the jungle. That's good.

Text.SourceString: The jungle provides, human friend. Taste its fruits with care, for each has its own story and essence.
Text.LocalizedString: The jungle provides, human friend. Taste its fruits with care, for each has its own story and essence.

Text.SourceString: You forage like the creatures of the forest. It's wise to learn from nature's bounty.
Text.LocalizedString: You forage like the creatures of the forest. It's wise to learn from nature's bounty.

Text.SourceString: Ah, my small friend...you've tasted the jungle's bounty. Each fruit and herb holds its own secret flavor.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, my small friend...you've tasted the jungle's bounty. Each fruit and herb holds its own secret flavor.

Text.SourceString: Nature provides, but one must know where to look.
Text.LocalizedString: Nature provides, but one must know where to look.

Text.SourceString: Be mindful of what you eat from the jungle. Not all that is lush and inviting is friendly to outsiders.
Text.LocalizedString: Be mindful of what you eat from the jungle. Not all that is lush and inviting is friendly to outsiders.

Text.SourceString: You don't understand what they said.
Text.LocalizedString: You don't understand what they said.
